Resources

1) NodeJS docs -- http://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/
2) Node flume-rpc library -- https://github.com/recoset/node-flume-rpc

Instructions

1) Build node from source.
2) npm install http://github.com/recoset/node-thrift/tarball/v0.7.0-recoset
3) npm install flume-rpc
4) node scrape.js
5) echo 'http://www.google.com' | flume sink 'rpcSink("localhost")'